\newlabel{fig:summary}{{4}{21}{Summary of all analyses. Core paradigms test the communicative stress test concept across different conversational configurations. Validation analyses confirm the signal is person-specific, partially robust to prompt changes, and not attributable to base-model artifacts. Sensitivity analyses address potential confounds. $N = 64$}{figure.4}{}}
